Class RawStudyCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • mrmc.gui.RawStudyCard

  • public class RawStudyCard
extends java.lang.Object
    Panel for selecting modalities, displaying charts of data statistics, and performing MRMC variance analysis with data from pilot study raw data files.
    Version:
    2.0b
    Author:
    Xin He, Ph.D, Brandon D. Gallas, Ph.D, Rohan Pathare
